	<div class="posts">
	<a name="107990472130863019">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.nap.edu/readingroom/books/trust/">Trust In Cyberspace, Nat'l Academy Press, 1999</a>.&nbsp; This book is online, and the definitions and illustration of trustworthiness may be instructive.&nbsp; The report was produced in 1999 and has 352 pages.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#107990472130863019">Sunday, March 21, 2004</a></span></div>
