	<div class="posts">
	<a name="107990459266458150">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.research.att.com/%7Esmb/">Steven M. Bellovin</a>.&nbsp; This is Steven M. Bellovin's web page at ATT Labs Research.&nbsp; It is a nicely cool page, especially with the customs documents passing the returnees from Apollo 11 through the Honolulu U.S. Customs along with their rocks.  Also of interest is work of a NRC committee on Information System Trustworthiness and a current committee studying the privacy implications of authentication technologies.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#107990459266458150">Sunday, March 21, 2004</a></span></div>
<br>
